reviewText: Very cool item with some nostalgic footage from a time gone by. I am from Oregon and rent a cabin in the Central Cascade mountains that belongs to two retired USFS Rangers I know. The cabin has a nice collection of forestry dcor and memorabilia, including books, and some old movies to watch on DVD celebrating the outdoors. I bought this as a gift for their cabin and it makes a perfect addition.
This was a great documentary on the US Forest Service Park Ranger.  It brings back nostalgic TV for me.  It is a good wholesome family show.
